erge, according to people who have been involved in the discussions."," Oman looks to merge two sovereign wealth funds amid a slump in oil prices, according to people familiar with the talks."," Oman is considering a merger of its two main sovereign wealth funds amid a slump in oil prices, people familiar with the matter said.", A look at some of the key stories that were talked about in the Arab world in the past 24 hours.," Oman's government may merge itstwo main sovereign wealth funds as part of a regional strategy aimed at boosting investments amid lower oil prices, people familiar with the matter said.", The article is now available in its entirety:
