aks founder Julian Assange is a target for the United States government.," Wikileaks founder Julian Assange faces possible arrest in the US, CNN reports, despite the government having no active case against the website until now."," A guide to the Wikileaks website, which publishes secret US government documents, and to the reports that the US is planning to arrest Julian Assange."," Wikileaks founder Julian Assange may be arrested by US authorities in what would be the website's first direct federal action, reports CNN.", The BBC looks at how the news is being interpreted.
